OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospitals of North Midlands
OL,6,FPatients are being warned of long
OL,7,Fdelays as the University Hospitals of
OL,8,FNorth Midlands NHS Trust has declared
OL,9,Fa critical incident.
OL,11,FAmong the hospitals affected are the
OL,12,FRoyal Stoke University Hospital and
OL,13,Fthe County Hospital in Stafford.
OL,15,FThe trust says it is facing sustained
OL,16,Fpressure to services. In particular,
OL,17,FAccident and Emergency services are
OL,18,Fthe most badly affected.
