OL,6,FPatients wishing to attend hospital
OL,7,Fare being advised to only use A&E when
OL,8,Fin serious or life-threatening
OL,9,Femergencies.
OL,11,FA statement released by the Chief
OL,12,FOperating Officer Simon Evans states
OL,13,Fthat the demand for services has
OL,14,Fgreatly increased in the last three
OL,15,Fdays.
