OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospitals of North Midlands
OL,6,F"We are currently experiencing
OL,7,Fextremely high demand for all our
OL,8,Fservices. Both Royal Stoke University
OL,9,FHospital and County Hospital in
OL,10,FStafford have been under severe and
OL,11,Fsustained pressure for the last week ,
OL,12,Fbut we have seen even greater demands
OL,13,Fin the last three days.
OL,15,F"We have therefore taken the decision
OL,16,Fto declare a critical incident. This
OL,17,Fhelps us to take additional measures
OL,18,Fto maintain safe services for our
OL,19,Fpatients and those in the community
OL,20,Fwaiting for an ambulance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
