OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospitals of North Midlands
OL,6,FDr Matthew Lewis, the trust's Medical
OL,7,FDirector said: "During this time the
OL,8,Femergency departments will continue to
OL,9,Fsee the sickest patients first, which
OL,10,Fmeans, for some patients, there may be
OL,11,Fmuch longer delays than usual.
OL,13,F"We continue to ask the public to help
OL,14,Fus by only using A&E in a serious or
OL,15,Flife threatening emergency. When we're
OL,16,Fdischarging patients, we ask that
OL,17,Ftheir friends or loved ones pick them
OL,18,Fup from hospital as soon as possible
OL,19,Fand have everything they need at home.
